{comment: Key change: Dm → D#m}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[D#m]I pushed my soul in a deep dark hole and then I followed it [D#m]in
[D#m]I watched myself crawlin' out as I was a-[A#7]crawlin' in
[D#m]I got up so tight I [F#]couldn't unwind, I [B]saw so much I broke my [D#m]mind
[D#m]I just dropped in to [A#7]see what condition my condition [D#m]was in
{end_of_verse}

